    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, C2, D2, 04 April 17:00 UTC to 09 April 08:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>A polar low vil Monday 4.April 17 UTC develop in C2 and vil move southwest. At monday evening 21 UTC the center will be at D2. West of center the wind is expected at northeasterly up to severe gale force 9. The low is expected to weaken at early Tuesday morning 08 UTC.</description>
